Package com.moniuliuma.android.decode

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DecodeResult
    DecodeResult is an interface passed by ReadListener.onReadEvent to retrieve scanned data from the decoder.
    ReadListener
    This interface is used by the application to listen to the decoder's read event.
    StartListener
    This interface is used by the application to listen to the scan started event.
    StopListener
    This interface is used by the application to listen to the scan stopped event.
    TimeoutListener
    This interface is used by the application to listen to the scan timeout event.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Barcode  
    BarcodeDefaults
    BarcodeDefaults gives developers access to decoder related methods of the terminal.
    BarcodeManager
    BarcodeManager gives developers access to decoder related methods of the terminal.
    DecodeIntent
    The core components of an Android application (its activities, services, and broadcast receivers) are activated by intents.
    Property  
    Property.id
    id is the class that includes all the properties identifiers.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Symbology
    Symbology is an enumeration class defining constants for different barcode types.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConfigException
    ConfigException is used for configuration related errors.
    DecodeException
    DecodeException is used for decoder related errors.
